# AiSyncApp Privacy Policy

**Effective: April 7, 2026**

AiSyncApp ("we", "us") respects your privacy. This policy explains how we handle data for Facebook/Instagram operations.

### Data We Collect
- **Meta Tokens**: Page/User Access Tokens (injected at runtime, never stored in agents).
- **Page Data**: Posts, DMs, Insights (processed transiently for actions).
- **Receipts**: Action logs (ID, timestamp, status, credits) stored in Supabase for billing/audit.

### How We Use Data
- Execute social ops (post, reply, insights).
- Billing via credit economy.
- Idempotency (prevent duplicates via request_id).

### Sharing
No sharing/selling. Tokens isolated in n8n/Supabase.

### Deletion
Contact support@aisyncapp.com. User data deleted on request.

### Changes
We'll notify via app/email.
